## Storage Architecture

### Data Layout

```
workspace/
└── .indexed/                    # Index directory
    ├── config.toml             # Workspace config
    ├── faiss_index             # FAISS index file
    ├── faiss_index.mappings.pkl # ID mappings
    └── chunks_metadata.pkl     # Chunk metadata
```

### Persistence

**StorageService handles:**
- FAISS index serialization
- ID mapping persistence (pickle)
- Chunk metadata storage (pickle)
- Atomic save operations

**Legacy storage** (still supported):
```
data/
├── collections/
│   └── {collection}/
│       ├── documents/
│       └── indexes/
└── caches/
```

